    "## 18. Regression and Correlation\n",
    "\n",
    "Regression is closely related to correlation but they serve different purposes.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Correlation** ($r$):\n",
    "- Measures **strength of linear association**\n",
    "- Symmetric: $r(X,Y) = r(Y,X)$\n",
    "- Range: -1 to +1\n",
    "\n",
    "**Regression** ($\\beta_1$):\n",
    "- Models **functional predictive relationship**\n",
    "- Directional: $X \\rightarrow Y$\n",
    "- Units: change in Y per unit change in X\n",
    "\n",
    "This distinction is crucial!"
